<div class="news-title"><div><h3>News</h3></div></div><dl class="news">
<dt>Sept 3, 2007</dt><dd>Version 3.1 released. Now includes versions for Java 6.0</dd>
<dt>Nov 11, 2006</dt><dd>Version 3.0 released. Now includes versions for Java 1.2, 1.3, 1.4, and 5.0 (sic!)</dd>
